ds the tall and narrow and are very regular and evenly spaced.  P and R are open, O is somewhat ovoid, E has bars of equal length, D is quite full, the diagonal of the N does not always start from the top of the first hasta. Interpuncts are not consistently used, with one elegant example in line 2",[41,48],{"type":42,"l":43,"from":44,"to":45,"h":46,"unit":47,"atLeast":46,"atMost":46},"letterHeight","Lines 1-6","line1","line6","72","mm",{"type":49,"l":50,"from":44,"to":51,"h":52,"unit":47},"interlinear","Line 1-2","line2","not measured",{"_":54,"notBefore":55,"notAfter":56,"evidence":57},"later 2nd or 3rd century CE (Vallarino on palaeographic grounds)",151,300,"lettering",[59,64],{"_":60,"type":61,"ref":62,"region":63},"Agrigentum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462086","Sicilia",{"_":65,"type":66,"ref":67,"region":63},"Agrigento","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6541860",[69],[70,71],37.32084,13.58876,[73,74],37.298238,13.589125,"Sicily",{"_":77,"role":78,"ref":79},"Museo Regionale Archeologico Pietro Griffo","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/130",{"type":81},"inventory",{"_":83,"mainLang":84,"languages":85},"Latin","la",[83],{"n":87,"url":88,"height":89,"width":90,"desc":91,"surfaceType":92},"screen","ISic004373_tiled.tif","2767px","2562px","Image courtesy of Giulio Vallarino","front",[94],{"atLeast":95,"atMost":95},72,[97,98,99,100],"L'année épigraphique: revue des publications épigraphiques relatives a l'antiquité romaine., 1888-","Vallarino, 2017, L'epigrafe dall'area del Tempio ellenistico-romano","Vallarino, 2018, Un nuovo \"curator rei publicae\" Liparese da Agrigento","Vallarino, 2022, L'epigrafe del curator rei publicae Liparitanorum",[102,103,104,105],"R46KDTZX","7RXKANQI","C395ZWLV","9SN32HDD",[107,108,109,110,20,24,111,112,113,114,112,115,116,84],"isic004373","dedication by a curator of the res publica liparitanorum",{"_":12},"honorific","agrigentum","agrigento","sicilia","sicily","museo regionale archeologico pietro griffo",